ZH: 她很聪明，总是能很快地理解问题。
EN: She is very intelligent, always able to quickly grasp problems.

ZH: 我们班上有个聪明的学生，考试从来不挂科。
EN: There is a smart student in our class who never fails exams.

ZH: 他虽然聪明，但有时也会做一些蠢事。
EN: Although he is intelligent, he sometimes does stupid things.

ZH: 聪明的人懂得尊重他人的观点。
EN: Intelligent people know how to respect others' opinions.

ZH: 她的聪明和努力受到了老师的表扬。
EN: Her intelligence and hard work have been praised by the teacher.

ZH: 那位科学家在研究方面非常聪明。
EN: That scientist is very smart in his research.

ZH: 孩子们总是很聪明地学习新的知识。
EN: Children always learn new knowledge very intelligently.

ZH: 她的聪明才智使得她成为了公司的领导者。
EN: Her intelligence has made her a leader in the company.

ZH: 他的聪明和幽默使得他备受同事喜爱。
EN: His intelligence and humor make him very popular with colleagues.

ZH: 这个项目的成功离不开大家的聪明智慧。
EN: The success of this project relies on everyone's intelligence.

ZH: 孩子们总是能够聪明地解决问题。
EN: Children are always able to solve problems intelligently.

ZH: 那个学生很聪明，总是能提出很好的建议。
EN: That student is very intelligent and always comes up with good suggestions.

ZH: 她在考试中表现得非常聪明。
EN: She performed very intelligently in the exam.

ZH: 这本书的作者非常聪明，他的观点非常独到。
EN: The author of this book is very intelligent, and his views are very insightful.

ZH: 他的聪明让他在团队中脱颖而出。
EN: His intelligence makes him stand out in the team.

ZH: 在解决问题时，需要大家都发挥聪明才智。
EN: When solving problems, everyone needs to use their intelligence.

ZH: 这个团队里每个人的聪明都必不可少。
EN: The intelligence of everyone in this team is essential.

ZH: 聪明的人懂得如何平衡工作和生活。
EN: Intelligent people know how to balance work and life.

ZH: 她的聪明赢得了老板的信任。
EN: Her intelligence has won the trust of the boss.

ZH: 他虽然聪明，但不懂得怎样处理人际关系。
EN: Although he is intelligent, he does not know how to deal with relationships.
